high_descs: Turn around and go to face the drying rack on the left side of the sink.
Pick the knife up from the drying rack.
Go to the sink on the right.
Slice the potato that is in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around and bring the potato slice to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and cook it.
Take the potato out and go to the recycling bin behind you.
Put the potato in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a piece of cooked potato.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the sink behind you.
Pick up the knife from the sink cutting board.
Take the knife to the sink.
Slice up the potato in the sink.
Leave the knife in the sink.
Pick up the left end slice of the potato.
Face the opposite direction and take the potato slice across the room to the microwave.
Cook the piece of potato in the microwave.
Face the opposite direction and cross the room to the wood counter.
Put the piece of potato in the green recycle bin under the counter. below the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of potato into a green recycle bin.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk toward the stove, then turn right at the counter, just after the kitchen sink
Pick up the knife on the dish drying mat, in front of the blue bowl.
Move over to your right, so that you are directly in front of the open sink.
Cut the potato that is inside the sink, into slices.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up the the slice form the left end of the potato.
Turn around and go to the microwave behind you.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, turn the microwave on, and remove the potato slice when the microwave turns off.
Turn to your left and walk towards the refrigerator, then turn to your left again just before the wall and walk to the light brown counter top.
Put the potato slice into the green recycle bin, under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato slice into the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the kitchen, make another right at the stove and walk to the covered portion of the sink, then turn to your left to face the window.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the blue bowl and apple.
Move over to the right, in front of the open portion of the sink, still facing the window.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Place the knife in the sink with the sliced potato.
Pick up a piece of the sliced potato.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right again at the wall and walk to the microwave.
Place the sliced portion of the potato in the microwave, heat it, then remove the potato from the microwave.
Turn to your left and walk to the wall, then turn left again at the wall and walk to the wooden counter top.
Place the heated potato slice in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato slice in the recycle bin.
